This project is a fork of Walter C. Pelissero tiff4cl

http://wcp.sdf-eu.org/software/tiff4cl-20090828.src.tbz
http://wcp.sdf-eu.org/software/

The file tiff.lisp was renamed to tiff4cl-tiff.lisp

The file util.lisp was renamed to tiff4cl-util.lisp

The file package.lisp was added.

The file README was added.

This file LICENSE was added. 
It consolidates the GLPL license header originally found at head of each file in
the original tiff4cl system.

The file tiff4cl-specials.lisp was added.
It contains definitions for special variables orginally found in tiff.lisp

The file tiff4cl-conditions.lisp was added.
It contains condition definitions orginally found in tiff.lisp

The file tiff4cl-floats.lisp was added.
It contains code orignally found in code.lisp from Pelissero's ie3fp system
The file tiff4cl-floats.lisp retains its original LGPL license.

